  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the air fryer to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. In a bowl, mix together zesty mayonnaise and beaten egg until well combined.",
    "3. Dip each fish delight into the egg mixture and then coat with crispy egg roll wrappers.",
    "4. Place the coated fish delights in the air fryer basket, leaving some space between each.",
    "5. Cook for 8-10 minutes or until the wrappers are golden brown and crispy.",
    "6. Remove from the air fryer and sprinkle with salt and black pepper.",
    "7. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
